# Node 20 via nvm
- Always switch to `node 20` via `nvm` before running `npm install` / `npm run dev` / `npm run build`.
- Use the command: `nvm use 20`.
- Quick verification: `node -v` and `npm -v`.
- If you need to change the Node version, follow the constraint in `package.json` (engine `>=20`).
